// 股票的每个时间点都是变化的，数组的每一项就是每个时间点的股票价格。求如何买卖才能赚到最多。
const greedy = (array) => {
  let last;
  return array.reduce((money, item) => {
    if (last && item > last) {
      const finalMoney = money + item - last;
      last = item;
      return finalMoney;
    }
    last = item;
    return money;
  }, 0);
}

console.log(greedy([7, 1, 5, 3, 6, 4]));
console.log(greedy([1, 2, 3, 4, 5]));
console.log(greedy([5, 4, 3, 2, 1]));
